.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHujkN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCHujkN.gif&h=37db3acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Do9jmF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Do9jmF.jpg&h=efc8703c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys8JoOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys8JoOj.png&h=2d0ace40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"f76a69748fe95ad666c75f89fd3b73c23870f7e7","tid":1602242,"uid":91519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"Good idea"},{"pid":"178f10efd1368595d6fb09c747432d6631bad55c","tid":1602242,"uid":217249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:53:15.000Z","msg":"係欣澳站兩條橋嘅玻璃後面睇風景都係一個唔錯選擇"},{"pid":"07d9bf293d2db3dd4a592950ee2c026319616cde","tid":1602242,"uid":306337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"又係機場撚 前兩次經歷仲學唔精?"},{"pid":"fc8046e5f5710345d218ad55617bccdadcdf137f","tid":1602242,"uid":241844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d9bf293d2db3dd4a592950ee2c026319616cde","tid":1602242,"uid":306337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"又係機場撚 前兩次經歷仲學唔精?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"同機場1.0要樣 今日幫大家燒起左團火<br />\n一把人係請左聽日連放4日 <br />\n一堆人包括我嬲到可以隨時罷工<br />\n<br />\n今日，我相信香港人足夠憤怒 唔係咩？"},{"pid":"387a881cc5d230e51b76afe80ede72b4f6501697","tid":1602242,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"一於機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275781a969d06bb10bb26aaec83c80959253e5e1","tid":1602242,"uid":241844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":